❯ what key allows me to sprint?                                                 

  Called thirdperson-game-iq (ctrl+o to expand)

● Left Shift — IMC_Default maps IA_Sprint to LeftShift.

  For reference, the full key mapping in IMC_Default:
  - Jump: Space Bar / Gamepad Face Button Bottom (A/Cross)
  - Move: WASD + Arrow Keys / Gamepad Left Stick
  - Look: Gamepad Right Stick (mouse look comes from the separate IMC_MouseLook
  context)
  - DoubleJump: J
  - Sprint: Left Shift
  - There's also an unmapped binding on L (no action assigned)

  Note there's no explicit IA_Sprint handler visible in
  BP_ThirdPersonCharacter's Blueprint graphs (unlike Move/Aim/DoubleJump) —
  sprint logic is likely implemented in the native C++ base class rather than
  Blueprint, so I can't tell you exactly what sprinting does (speed multiplier,
  stamina, etc.) from this index alone.

